{"title":"New Bontrager Foray & Evoke MTB shoes join Cadence Spin shoes for varied terrain","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/17/new-bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-shoes-step-into-gravel-cyclocross-too/","date":1616039752000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Looking for one cycling shoe for all your offroad riding? The new Bontrager Foray aims to be the best shoe for gravel, cyclocross and mountain biking thanks to abundant tread, toe protection, and a stiff-yet-walkable sole.</p><p>With a $159.99 MSRP and four understated colors, it hits a nice mid point for price and features in a shoe that works for a lot of things. Here’s the details…</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105755/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105755/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-4.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager foray mountain bike and gravel shoe tread details\" width=\"1471\" height=\"467\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1471px) 100vw, 1471px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105755/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-4.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105755/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-4.jpg 1471w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105755/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-4-297x94.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105755/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-4-800x254.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.