</a></p><p>The upper is full synthetic with a forefoot Velcro closure and BOA L6 dial to cinch up the rest. Perforations allow heat to escape off the sides and top.</p><p>The raised GnarGuard rubberized coating does more than cap the toes, running down the sides about half way back.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager foray mountain bike and gravel shoe upper and closure details from a different angle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105807/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-5-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Bontrager’s InForm Race last has proven comfortable on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/12/12/review-bontragers-wavecell-velocis-helmets-cambion-mountain-bike-shoes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">other shoes we’ve tested</a>, leaving plenty of room for your toes to adjust and spread on longer rides, but maintain a snug capture in the heel for spirited pedaling.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p>It gets a nylon composite sole with a rated stiffness of 6 out of 14, so they should be easy to walk in without tiring your feet out on longer, harder rides. We just received a set for testing, stay tuned to see how that pans out.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager foray mountain bike and gravel shoe BOA L6 dial details\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-bike-gravel-shoe-details-1-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/17105717/bontrager-foray-mountain-