MTB shoe\" width=\"766\" height=\"539\" sizes=\"(max-width: 766px) 100vw, 766px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2.jpg 766w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-297x209.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-696x490.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-597x420.jpg 597w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-100x70.jpg 100w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2.jpg 766w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-297x209.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-696x490.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-597x420.jpg 597w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111257/Bontrager-Evoke-mountain-bike-shoe-2-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>Along with the Foray, the Bontrager Evoke has been redesigned to ditch the velcro in favor of a single BOA dial. The BOA L6 dial allows for micro-adjustments while riding, and combines with a roomier inForm Race last for a comfortable fit. Details include a perforated upper with a GnarGuard rubberized coating on the toe and heel, and a Tachyon rubber sole for plenty of grip off the bike.</p><p>Even with the addition of the BOA, the Evoke is priced at just $119.99.</p><h2><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span>Bontrager Cadence Spin Bike Shoe</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle.jpg\" alt=\"Bontrager Cadence spin bike shoe \" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle.jpg 600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle-120x80.jpg 120w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle.jpg 600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/19111010/Bontrager-Cadence-Spin-bike-shoe-trainer-fitness-sneaker-bicycle-120x80.jpg 120w\"></a></p><p>Bontrager’s new shoes aren’t only confined to the mountain bike/offroad space. For those that want a shoe for&nbsp;<em>indoo</em><em>r</em> riding, the all new Cadence Spin bike Shoe could fit the bill. Designed with a balance of function and fashion, the SPD compatible shoe uses a standard two bolt cleat to allow for a walkable shoe that still provides a solid connection to the pedals. If you’re tired of slipping on hardwood floors in your Peloton Shoes, swap out the pedals and throw on a pair of spin bike shoes like these that are closer to your sneakers.</p><p>Built with a slip-on mesh upper and a single BOA L6 dial, the shoes add extra comfort with an EVA foam midsole. You can pick up a pair of Cadence shoes for $134.99.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=0d15472d-796a-41f7-afb4-32437118891b&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trekbikes.com%2Fus%2Fen_US%2Fbike-clothing%2Fcycling-shoes%2Fmountain-bike-shoes%2Fbontrager-foray-mountain-bike-shoe%2Fp%2F25341%2F%3FcolorCode%3Dblack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Bontrager.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"26a239f2327b8ef7316af09fbf6c26cbe9ae50c51448e3792e85a7416d8b9410","category":"Cycling"}